dns-update (1.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add a CLI-only delete mode for removing managed A, AAAA, or both record
    families without probing current egress IPs.
  * Keep single-family deletion targeted by using dedicated provider delete
    planning and verification instead of normal reconciliation.
  * Bump the runtime user-agent and package metadata to 1.3.0.

