dns-update (1.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Add a CLI-only force-push mode that refreshes matching DNS records even
    when the observed egress IPs have not changed.
  * Document the new force-push flag, release behavior, and packaging notes.
  * Bump the runtime user-agent and package metadata to 1.2.0.

